# ─── acpx_auto_tester_test agent runtime ─────────────────────────────
# All agent runtime files (campaign state, locks, dispatcher logs,
# per-issue state.json / attempt_state.json / log/ / summary.md) live
# under the agent runtime root and must NEVER be committed. The default
# basename is `ifp-result/`; projects that pass `result_basename=<name>`
# in the trigger should replace the entry below with the matching name
# (e.g. `pts-result/`). The agent additionally writes the chosen
# basename into `.git/info/exclude` per-clone, so this `.gitignore`
# entry is belt-and-suspenders rather than strictly required.
#
# The ONLY exception is each issue's output directory
# `<runtime-root>/issue-<iid>/hulat-spec-issue<iid>/`, which the agent
# explicitly force-adds via `git add -f` in stage_and_guard.sh —
# that bypasses this gitignore for the single allowed path.
ifp-result/

# ─── Common local noise ─────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
